      <title>下雪总是孩子们的最爱</title>
      <link>https://iliu.org/4010.html</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jan 2022 07:17:04 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://iliu.org/4010.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;尽管昨天一阵鸡飞狗跳的忙碌，尽管晚上接女儿的时候是偷偷溜出去的，但是接到女儿的时候，她还是非常的兴奋。原因有二，一是，大雪纷飞，终于见到了期盼已久的大雪，二是，明天又可以宅家里上课了。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>尽管昨天一阵鸡飞狗跳的忙碌，尽管晚上接女儿的时候是偷偷溜出去的，但是接到女儿的时候，她还是非常的兴奋。原因有二，一是，大雪纷飞，终于见到了期盼已久的大雪，二是，明天又可以宅家里上课了。</p>
<p>下雪天，总少不了拍几张图片<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="850" height="1018" src="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/d9706105b9db9e2.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-4011" srcset="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/d9706105b9db9e2.jpg 850w, https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/d9706105b9db9e2-768x920.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" /> <figcaption>昏黄的路灯下，纷纷扬扬的大雪，以及被灯光照亮的几根树枝</figcaption></figure> <figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="850" height="637" src="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2c37ae06851eb5d.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-4012" srcset="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2c37ae06851eb5d.jpg 850w, https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2c37ae06851eb5d-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" /><figcaption>那雪，合着北风，铺面而来</figcaption></figure> <figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="850" height="1133" src="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1ed6e6d901abae9.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-4013" srcset="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1ed6e6d901abae9.jpg 850w, https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1ed6e6d901abae9-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" /><figcaption>树上也积满了雪花，2022年郑州大雪</figcaption></figure> <figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="850" height="799" src="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/7321f8c084d4b98.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-4014" srcset="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/7321f8c084d4b98.jpg 850w, https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/7321f8c084d4b98-768x722.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" /><figcaption>女儿手工制作的爱心</figcaption></figure></p>
